title: ASEAN-Australia-New Zealand Free Trade Agreement (AANZFTA)
description: A year since the ASEAN-Australia-New Zealand Free Trade Agreement (AANZFTA) came into force, business leaders reflect on the opportunities it has created so far. Principal economist of the Asian Development Bank, Dr Ganeshan Wignaraja says it is only the beginning.
channelTitle: Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade
